title: Orlando Acevedo Charry
text:
Welcome to my site!
I am a PhD candidate in Interdisciplinary Ecology (SNRE) with concentration in Wildlife Ecology and Conservation, advised by Dr. Miguel Acevedo. I am also part of the Florida Museum of Natural History, co-advised by Dr. Scott Robinson, and the Tropical Conservation and Development program.
